In re Jeffrey McArthur Carter EL-BEY. No. 166P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 11, 2007.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 10th day of April 2007 by Petitioner for "Petition for Writ of Prohibition":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 11th day of April 2007."
